    "gp_section_608112356739777434": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "3ad40c9ee78d308e7aa03ae7324b14587bccb20e4a10802af5a068524cb9195e_1_1_0_0__1",
        "ggVIobg_dhe_text": "<p>It was something far older. A delivery method our grandparents used routinely. One that bypasses the stomach entirely and reaches the intestinal wall directly — where parasites actually live.</p>",
        "ggWdyfFN3DU_text": "<p>But what Sarah Whitfield showed him that morning wasn't failure.</p>",
        "gg_6svzOBi7_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/istockphoto-1147544807-612x612_copy.jpg",
        "ggiO5AWU0es_text": "<p>Finally breaking apart. Finally releasing. Finally coming out.</p>",
        "ggihbwY3P5__text": "<p>Biofilm. The invisible fortress that had been protecting parasites inside Sarah's intestinal wall for years — hiding them from her immune system, from lab tests, from every doctor, supplement, and elimination diet she'd tried.</p>",
        "ggj7Vm-UNaG_text": "<p>There, in the toilet, were rope-like masses. Mucus-covered. Dense. Unmistakable.</p>",
        "ggn1gbAGt5U_text": "<p>But first, let me show you exactly how bad it got.</p>",
        "ggpGP2uv-b6_text": "<p>It was a Wednesday in March. Ten days into what Gary had assumed was just another failed experiment in a two-year string of them.</p>",
        "ggu2H7mQNou_text": "<p><i>\"We just held each other and cried. Two years of doctors saying it's just IBS. Two years of eliminating food after food. And the answer had been parasites hiding behind biofilm the entire time.\"</i> — Gary Whitfield, 46, Austin, TX</p>",
        "ggvL3mfWHHm_text": "<p>What Gary discovered — and what ultimately ended his wife's nightmare — wasn't a new drug, a new diet, or a new supplement.</p>",
        "ggxCXeVESn3_text": "<p>Gary Whitfield will never forget the morning his wife called him into the bathroom, face white as a sheet, hands shaking.</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-608112356739777434"
    },
    "gp_section_608114683991294550": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "1849057596b7a48f64293c28bd28909d10eb7c0ee26bfa02138f5a62cafcf843_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg1XAPWYMYi_text": "<p>⚠️ $2,800 on food sensitivity panels (\"avoid gluten and dairy\")</p>",
        "gg7sLIn1wnL_text": "<p>3. Lexapro (\"anxiety\")</p>",
        "gg9dt0zok7__text": "<p>The symptoms arrived like uninvited guests that refused to leave:</p>",
        "ggA9GWxHXdn_text": "<p><i>\"We spent twenty-three thousand dollars to be told nothing was wrong. The answer cost us forty-four dollars.\" — </i>Gary Whitfield</p>",
        "ggB5I-3tNac_text": "<p>7. OTC Ibuprofen (headaches from the brain fog)</p>",
        "ggEpRg8mXN1_text": "<p><i>\"Middle-age hormones. Happens to most women. Try probiotics.</i>\" — Sarah's primary care physician</p>",
        "ggHXN6KqF2W_text": "<p>When Sarah Stopped Being Sarah</p>",
        "ggJhmS1lkq8_text": "<p>The breaking point came on a Tuesday night. Sarah sat on the edge of the bed, crying, and said five words that broke Gary's heart:</p>",
        "ggKRwc6O5IK_text": "<p>⚠️ $9,600 on IBS medications over 2 years</p>",
        "ggLOtGJQTjR_text": "<p>2. Omeprazole (acid reflux)</p>",
        "ggM9Ybm7vZi_text": "<p><i>\"They had a pill for every symptom. But not one doctor ever asked why I was having all of them at the same time.\" — </i>Sarah Whitfield</p>",
        "ggNlsCqdur4_text": "<p>⚠️ $4,200 on functional medicine consultations</p>",
        "ggPdnArLvhG_text": "<p>Fiber made it worse. By year two, Sarah's medicine cabinet looked like a pharmacy:</p>",
        "ggSG32grfwV_text": "<p>❌ Dry, itchy patches no cream could fix</p>",
        "ggTzoKU1z18_text": "<p>4. Hydroxyzine (sleep)</p>",
        "ggU9xzpND8D_text": "<p>5. Miralax (constipation from the other meds)</p>",
        "ggXwLwgmPXK_text": "<p>Before finding the answer, the Whitfield’s spent:</p>",
        "ggZpXN4lA7p_text": "<p>❌ Exhaustion that eight hours of sleep couldn't touch</p>",
        "ggbGZHnqM74_text": "<p>❌ Sugar cravings at exactly the same time every afternoon</p>",
        "ggbfQTmkbn-_text": "<p>❌ Skin tags appearing on her neck</p>",
        "ggbs7JmAssX_text": "<p>⚠️ $3,200 on colonoscopy (\"just inflammation\")</p>",
        "ggd_M28mbfM_text": "<p>$89 probiotics did nothing. Neither did digestive enzymes. Neither did the elimination diets that slowly stripped every joy from eating. The gastroenterologist's verdict: \"IBS. Manage your stress. Eat more fiber.\"</p>",
        "ggdl6Kslfu2_text": "<p>1. Dicyclomine (IBS cramping)</p>",
        "ggiqE_SBQZP_text": "<p>❌ Feeling \"crawly\" sensations under her skin at night</p>",
        "ggj06GNzH3Q_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/istockphoto-1147544807-612x612_copy.jpg",
        "ggkUxnOY1xy_text": "<p>❌ Brain fog so thick she'd forget words mid-sentence</p>",
        "ggnCNIjY22n_text": "<p>❌ 3 AM wake-ups — every single night, like clockwork</p>",
        "ggnFBvleaj9_text": "<p>⚠️ $1,800 on probiotics and digestive enzymes</p>",
        "ggnz7-QQmxU_text": "<p><i>\"I'm broken. What's wrong with me?\"</i></p>",
        "ggopjhTuGvm_text": "<p>❌ Bloating so severe she looked six months pregnant by 2 PM every day</p>",
        "ggqHX3BDP0h_text": "<p>❌ Teeth grinding that cracked a molar</p>",
        "ggqo9rfLJ3B_text": "<p>The medical carousel started spinning. Each symptom earned a new specialist, a new test, a new label — and a new prescription.</p>",
        "ggrCD5lKcd4_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/istockphoto-1147544807-612x612_copy.jpg",
        "gguGzhmjnWF_text": "<p>6. Metamucil (fiber — the thing making it worse)</p>",
        "ggyuj3m3c4O_text": "<p>Sarah Whitfield used to be the kind of woman who ran the room — sharp, funny, managed a 15-person marketing team, trained for half-marathons, never missed a school event. But by 45, something shifted. And it never shifted back.</p>",
        "ggyvaFdF51S_text": "<p>⚠️ $1,400 on elimination diet coaching</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-608114683991294550"
    },
    "gp_section_608116654307541559": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "de27863c77cecfb97e1539e17bd4829441c949bbb14260bc38d60d65b1f11f45_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg0JBGWcdod_text": "<p><i>\"Sarah hadn't traveled anywhere unusual. She ate organic. Drank filtered water. Did everything 'right.' But she'd been accumulating parasites her entire life — from food, from the family dog, from the garden she loved. By the time symptoms appeared, they'd built a biofilm fortress so dense that no test could find them and no pill could reach them.\" — </i>Gary Whitfield</p>",
        "gg1dImRl53f_text": "<p>Here's how Americans contract parasites every single day, without ever leaving home:</p>",
        "gg3VScOLM1l_text": "<p>❌ Pets — dogs, cats, and household animals shed parasitic eggs in their fur and feces. A face licks. A shared couch. That's all it takes.</p>",
        "gg6jENo6EnM_text": "<p>The 3 AM Discovery That Changed Everything</p>",
        "gg6qiBKNdJw_text": "<p>Most people assume parasites are a \"third-world problem.\" Something you get on a trip to Southeast Asia. Something that couldn't happen in suburban Austin.</p>",
        "gg7N0Y6EXEm_text": "<p>According to the World Health Organization, over 85% of Americans are living with some form of parasitic infection — most without knowing it.</p>",
        "ggAIevyKfxE_text": "<p>❌ Contaminated water — tap water, well water, lake water. Municipal treatment doesn't eliminate all parasitic cysts.</p>",
        "ggEPeMVqJew_text": "<p>Four months in, he found a line in a parasitology study that made him drop his phone:</p>",
        "ggFCv22-qBx_text": "<p><i>\"Parasite’s burrow into the mucosal lining and secrete a protective biofilm matrix that shields them from host immune response, standard diagnostic detection, and orally-administered antiparasitic compounds.\"</i></p>",
        "ggFDE9xqTJd_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/istockphoto-1147544807-612x612_copy.jpg",
        "ggFaTYc5VDL_text": "<p>The WHO has quietly classified certain parasites as Group 1 carcinogens — the same category as cigarettes and asbestos. Yet American doctors rarely test for parasites unless you've recently visited a developing country.</p>",
        "ggHptSZWFVk_text": "<p>You don't need to travel anywhere exotic. You just need to eat food, drink water, touch an animal, or walk outside. Which means virtually everyone is exposed — repeatedly — throughout their lives.</p>",
        "ggNMJcHcQDO_text": "<p>❌ Insect bites — mosquitoes, ticks, and flies transmit parasitic organisms directly into the bloodstream.</p>",
        "ggOwl-lgGbr_text": "<p>Standard stool tests miss 70-90% of biofilm-protected infections. The parasites don't shed consistently. So when your doctor says \"everything looks normal\" — that means almost nothing.</p>",
        "ggVut1rWmK2_text": "<p><i>\"That was Sarah. Every single symptom. The bloating — because they're inflaming her gut wall. The 3 AM wake-ups — because parasites are most active between 1 and 4 AM. The brain fog — from their toxic metabolic waste. The sugar cravings — because that's what they feed on. And not one doctor in two years thought to test for it.\" —</i> Gary Whitfield</p>",
        "ggeYkvStKQh_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/istockphoto-1147544807-612x612_copy.jpg",
        "gghp69xmLyT_text": "<p>Gary read it four times.</p>",
        "ggjraXEKnc9_text": "<p>❌ Person-to-person contact — shared food, shared bathrooms, daycare centers, intimate contact.</p>",
        "ggk94nhsM58_text": "<p>That assumption is dangerously wrong.</p>",
        "gglmimGh4Cu_text": "<p>The difference between someone who shows symptoms and someone who doesn't? The size of the colony. The strength of the immune system. And whether the parasites have had time to establish biofilm — the fortress that makes them nearly impossible to detect or remove.</p>",
        "ggvuF2CppEt_text": "<p>❌ Unwashed produce — lettuce, berries, herbs. Soil-borne parasites cling to surfaces that a quick rinse can't remove.</p>",
        "ggy342TP1DM_text": "<p>❌ Walking barefoot — hookworm larvae in soil penetrate through the soles of your feet.</p>",
        "ggy4i5KnAG-_text": "<p>The Uncomfortable Truth: Over 85% of Americans Are Carrying Parasites Right Now</p>",
        "ggyCXdrfhS5_text": "<p>❌ Undercooked meat and fish — sushi, rare steaks, deli meats. Parasite larvae survive anything below thorough cooking temperatures.</p>",
        "ggyjAv5S92b_text": "<p>Gary barely slept anymore. Most nights he'd lie awake scrolling through medical journals and research forums, searching for anything the doctors might have missed.</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-608116654307541559"
    },
    "gp_section_608117581718487812": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "2c64530aa129eae223035f91be622a89d743a4cd936d0d48c29bc7f3dbb03a78_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg-yUHcdK2__text": "<p>2. Compression — consistent pressure against the skin increases absorption 2 to 4 times. The castor oil must be pressed into the abdominal skin, not loosely draped.</p>",
        "gg17M_MfMBN_text": "<p>When you swallow a capsule — any capsule — stomach acid breaks it down. The surviving compounds get absorbed into the bloodstream through the small intestine. By the time anything reaches the lower intestinal wall where parasites burrow, it's been diluted to near-nothing.</p>",
        "gg3uURn9i8K_text": "<p>Through the skin, it bypasses stomach acid entirely. It absorbs through the dermal layers, penetrates into the intestinal wall tissue, and arrives at the biofilm matrix intact. Full-strength. Undiluted.</p>",
        "gg47TI_3aVW_text": "<p>✅ Penetrates and dissolves biofilm matrices — breaking apart the protective shield</p>",
        "gg7LDf-Qh87_text": "<p>Gary needed something that could bypass the stomach entirely and reach the gut wall directly.</p>",
        "gg7l-bZmrYE_text": "<p>✅ Stimulates lymphatic drainage in the abdominal cavity by up to 60%</p>",
        "gg8F9vc699Q_text": "<p>Here's what modern peer-reviewed research confirms:</p>",
        "gg9gKAnrV9G_text": "<p>Sarah's sister Diane found it first — in a gut health community online. Women describing overnight castor oil packs that actually worked. No mess. No complication. Results within weeks.</p>",
        "ggDeVCNF9ld_text": "<p>It's not that the supplements are bad. It's that the oral delivery pathway cannot reach parasites embedded behind biofilm in the intestinal wall.</p>",
        "ggE9ybVXbf8_text": "<p>The compound is called ricinoleic acid. It makes up 90% of castor oil's fatty acid content. It's been used medicinally since ancient Egypt. Hippocrates prescribed it. Your great-grandmother likely had a bottle in her cabinet.</p>",
        "ggEUQoAQZii_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/istockphoto-1147544807-612x612_copy.jpg",
        "ggGpBlrdOku_text": "<p>What he found had been hiding in plain sight for a thousand years.</p>",
        "ggHS5txqzxC_text": "<p>3. Body heat — heat opens pores and accelerates transdermal delivery. During sleep, core temperature rises naturally. A properly fitted pack captures that heat.</p>",
        "ggLFMYOHAFI_text": "<p>✅ Stays in place all night — even for restless sleepers</p>",
        "ggMRJy8OQm3_text": "<p>✅ Creates a hostile environment for parasitic organisms in gut wall tissue</p>",
        "ggMRPP363FY_text": "<p>✅ Body heat capture — no external heating pad needed. No auto-shutoff.</p>",
        "ggOJsveCdPr_text": "<p>The Invisible Wall No Pill Can Penetrate</p>",
        "ggORDTN0FNc_text": "<p>This is why our grandparents used castor oil PACKS — not pills. Cloth soaked in castor oil, wrapped around the abdomen, worn to bed.<br>They didn't have the science. They just knew it worked. And somewhere between their generation and ours, we forgot.</p>",
        "ggSKlyQkfA__text": "<p>✅ Organic cotton inner layer — absorbs and holds castor oil evenly without dripping or leaking</p>",
        "ggSlhuwBsJI_text": "<p>When castor oil is ingested, stomach acid converts ricinoleic acid into a simple laxative compound. That's all you get — cramping, diarrhea, and misery. The biofilm-dissolving properties, the lymphatic stimulation, the antimicrobial effects? All destroyed by digestion.</p>",
        "ggYSu2ZGAfW_text": "<p>1. Sustained contact — six to eight hours minimum. Overnight. While the body's temperature rises and pores open.</p>",
        "ggZ0JvWgbrV_text": "<p>✅ Leak-proof barrier — sheets stay completely clean. Every night.</p>",
        "ggZMmeptkQd_text": "<p>The System That Made Transdermal Delivery Possible</p>",
        "ggaES5QSYfw_text": "<p><i>\"I expected some complicated ritual. I applied the oil, wrapped the pack, went to sleep. Took it off in the morning. Sheets clean. That's it. That's the whole thing.\" — </i>Sarah Whitfield</p>",
        "ggaSWmEfj5G_text": "<p>✅ Adjustable compression wrap — provides sustained pressure for deeper transdermal absorption</p>",
        "ggbKX78bFrr_text": "<p>✅ Triggers smooth muscle contractions in the intestinal wall</p>",
        "ggb_hnfxgci_text": "<p><strong>But here's the critical detail that changes everything:</strong></p>",
        "ggbcOUxipUL_text": "<p>But transdermal delivery requires three specific conditions:</p>",
        "ggdHGvhx2ah_text": "<p>✅ Crosses tissue barriers when applied topically under sustained pressure</p>",
        "ggeCV6ICgbR_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/istockphoto-1147544807-612x612_copy.jpg",
        "gghSAU_L2-C_text": "<p>The Ancient Compound Big Pharma Can't Patent — And Prays You Never Discover</p>",
        "gghdNsf223i_text": "<p>The product was called Tavio.</p>",
        "ggjFSXzl7r5_text": "<p>✅ 60-second application — apply oil, wrap the pack, go to sleep</p>",
        "ggjmW0ig-xO_text": "<p>The parasites behind the biofilm wall never even know you took anything.</p>",
        "ggk7ow-v0zJ_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#B22121;\"><strong>You cannot swallow castor oil and get these benefits.</strong></span></p>",
        "ggnm2nFNJmx_text": "<p>A purpose-built system engineered for overnight transdermal castor oil delivery:</p>",
        "ggoGHTyJXlw_text": "<p>✅ Reusable for months — one purchase, not a subscription</p>",
        "ggqQj8Itgva_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/istockphoto-1147544807-612x612_copy.jpg",
        "ggqSrI5rCUq_text": "<p><strong>Ricinoleic acid must be delivered transdermally — through the skin.</strong></p>",
        "ggsI6ZcWu-i_text": "<p>This is why elimination diets provide temporary relief but never resolve the bloating. This is why probiotic after probiotic fails. This is why people try cleanse after cleanse and quit saying \"it didn't work.\"</p>",
        "ggtiQEoMhDY_text": "<p>When parasites burrow into the intestinal wall, they secrete a sticky, mucus-like matrix around themselves. This biofilm is a fortress. Behind it, parasites are invisible to the immune system, undetectable by lab tests, and completely shielded from every oral supplement.</p>",
        "gguUcWlGBPG_text": "<p>Gary ordered it immediately. Sarah put it on that night.</p>",
        "ggyHdyNY48m_text": "<p>Biofilm is the key to understanding why nothing had worked for Sarah — and why nothing works for millions of Americans cycling through gut health products.</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-608117581718487812"
    },
    "gp_section_608124842226483972": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "116afb83fdcc34e5b55d95a843d77ddf69940168cbf741a2edf0330191d3e1fa_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg0C-GVpkzJ_text": "<p><i>\"Nothing worked. Every protocol. Every supplement. Every diet. Two weeks with the pack and I ate bread for the first time in two years. I wept into a dinner roll and I'm not ashamed of it.\" — </i>Linda K., Austin, TX</p>",
        "gg0odANFluB_text": "<p>The Neighborhood That Woke Up</p>",
        "gg1LoQ2bACh_text": "<p><strong>Day 35: </strong>Follow-up with her gastroenterologist. \"Your symptoms are completely resolved. What did you do?\" Sarah told him about the biofilm and the castor oil pack. He wrote \"alternative treatment\" in her file and moved on.</p>",
        "gg26ZnNME5g_text": "<p>That's what the pack does. That's all it does. And it's enough.</p>",
        "gg3G5Ay2cup_text": "<p>If you or someone you love is living with bloating that never goes away, 3 AM wake-ups, and an \"IBS\" diagnosis that leads nowhere — consider this:</p>",
        "gg3NkJSgS9M_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/istockphoto-1147544807-612x612_copy.jpg",
        "gg3aLqH4LfR_text": "<p>The Numbers That Should Make You Angry</p>",
        "gg3zUFh2joK_text": "<p>She sleeps through the night. Every night. She still wears her Tavio pack to bed. Sixty seconds to put on. Takes it off in the morning.</p>",
        "gg4CD9gHRfm_label": "<p>CLAIM YOUR TAVIO PACK NOW — WHILE STILL AVAILABLE</p>",
        "gg5mNwEuw-0_text": "<p>A reusable castor oil pack that costs $44 and works while you sleep doesn't generate gastroenterology visits. Doesn't sell monthly prescriptions. Doesn't create lifelong supplement customers.</p>",
        "gg6fzPBnYgu_text": "<p>The local pharmacy reported a noticeable decline in IBS medication refills. Sarah's gastroenterologist noted several patients with \"spontaneous improvement.\" He didn't investigate further.</p>",
        "gg9qmIL2AYJ_text": "<p>Sarah Whitfield is 47 now. She runs her team again. Trains for a 10K. Eats whatever she wants — pasta, bread, dessert — without unbuttoning her pants or mapping the nearest bathroom.</p>",
        "gg9ve8grKft_text": "<p><strong>P.S. </strong><i>Gary wanted us to add this: \"If you're reading this and you're thinking 'that's my wife' — you're right. It was my wife too. The bloating. The wake-ups. The IBS label. She wasn't broken. She had parasites hiding behind biofilm that no doctor tested for and no pill could reach. The pack reached them. Forty-four dollars and twenty-one days. Don't wait two years like I did.\"</i></p>",
        "ggAoatJDdwk_text": "<p><strong>Days 19-21:</strong> Sarah ate pasta, bread, and dessert for dinner. Woke up flat. No bloating. No pain. She cried at the breakfast table. Happy tears.</p>",
        "ggCOfZCYydj_text": "<p><strong>The chronic gut symptom management industry: over </strong><span style=\"color:#B22121;\"><strong>$24 billion a year.</strong></span></p>",
        "ggDRU4-RkAZ_text": "<p>The Transformation That Stunned Everyone</p>",
        "ggEk-8-bbGq_text": "<p>Sarah's proof. Jen's proof. Tom's wife is proof. Mike's proof. Linda's proof.</p>",
        "ggFh_9PDdnd_text": "<p><i>\"Two years. Seven medications. Twenty-three thousand dollars. And he wrote 'alternative treatment' and didn't even ask what it was.\" — </i>Gary Whitfield</p>",
        "ggG89c282X-_text": "<p>It's not IBS. It's parasites hiding behind biofilm in the intestinal wall. No pill can reach them there. They need to be reached transdermally. Through the skin. With sustained compression and body heat. Overnight.</p>",
        "ggGoo4SQSb1_text": "<p>✅ Week 3-4: Biofilm expulsion — visible mucus-like strands passing</p>",
        "ggKdu0dGUeO_text": "<p><i>\"Three weeks with the pack. We went to a steakhouse for our anniversary. Full meal. Steak, sides, bread, dessert. No bloating. No bathroom emergency. She ordered dessert and I nearly cried watching her eat without fear.\" — </i>Tom R., Austin, TX</p>",
        "ggMnGs6WadP_text": "<p>The IBS medication market generates $1.8 billion annually. Gut health supplements: $3.2 billion. Gastroenterology visits: $4.7 billion. Colonoscopies: $14.7 billion.</p>",
        "ggOY3aNyV3p_text": "<p>$44 | Reusable for Months | Free Shipping | 90-Day Money Back Guarantee</p>",
        "ggPCC13Sf8y_text": "<p><strong>Days 1-3:</strong> Increased gurgling and abdominal activity. \"Things are moving in there,\" Sarah said. \"For the first time in years, something is actually happening.\"</p>",
        "ggPXpKle-Pk_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/istockphoto-1147544807-612x612_copy.jpg",
        "ggQIon4Nzge_text": "<p><strong>Days 11-14:</strong> Bloating dropped dramatically. Could button her jeans all day. Wore a fitted top to work for the first time in two years.</p>",
        "ggQPsiEVJH4_text": "<p><strong>Days 15-18:</strong> The 3 AM wake-ups stopped. Sarah slept through the night for the first time in two years. Gary woke at 6 AM and she was still sleeping. He lay there in silence — not because he couldn't sleep, but because he couldn't believe she finally could.</p>",
        "ggQRcG27qCj_text": "<p>Every one of those dollars depends on people managing symptoms instead of addressing the root cause.</p>",
        "ggQYOM9PUXO_text": "<p>Within three months, seventeen families in Gary and Sarah's circle were using the pack nightly. The pattern was unmistakable:</p>",
        "ggSWo3WL1yx_text": "<p><i>\"I'm not the bloated, exhausted zombie anymore. I'm not the woman afraid to eat, afraid to wear fitted clothes, afraid something was wrong with her that nobody could find. I'm me again. For the first time in years.\" — </i>Sarah Whitfield</p>",
        "ggU_0e1Z39C_text": "<p>Word spread the way it always does — one stunned conversation at a time.</p>",
        "ggWgGourZ1A_label": "<p>CLAIM YOUR TAVIO PACK NOW — WHILE STILL AVAILABLE</p>",
        "ggXptPLGM0y_text": "<p>What Sarah Says Now</p>",
        "ggYZhbryET6_text": "<p><i>\"They don't want you to fix it. They want you to manage it. Forever. At four hundred dollars a month.\" — </i>Gary Whitfield</p>",
        "gg_Emy7Z-2p_text": "<p>✅ Month 2: Complete resolution of chronic bloating, normalized sleep</p>",
        "ggaNyI4E_lW_text": "<p>Over 85% of Americans are carrying parasites right now. Most will never be tested. Their doctors will call it IBS, hormones, stress, anxiety. They'll prescribe pills for every symptom and never once ask why they're all happening at the same time.</p>",
        "ggawLGC8Zq__text": "<p>Three weeks from now, you could be proof too.</p>",
        "ggbVSCGwpjf_text": "<p><strong>Days 8-10: </strong>The morning that changed everything. Rope-like biofilm masses finally releasing. Years of buildup breaking apart. Sarah whispered: \"That was inside me this whole time. And every doctor said I was fine.\"</p>",
        "ggd-Js-VqnT_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/istockphoto-1147544807-612x612_copy.jpg",
        "ggdC47NMrXG_text": "<p>✅ Week 2-3: 3 AM wake-ups stopped</p>",
        "ggdq9gb4n9j_label": "<p>CLAIM YOUR TAVIO PACK NOW — WHILE STILL AVAILABLE</p>",
        "ggdsRwNtzlP_text": "<p>✅ Week 1: Increased gut activity, mobilization beginning</p>",
        "ggf2dTxWXNL_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/istockphoto-1147544807-612x612_copy.jpg",
        "ggfmy2ndDsF_text": "<p>✅ Week 2: Bloating reduction — most could button pants all day</p>",
        "gghKcIyDhhV_text": "<p><strong>Days 4-7:</strong> First reduction in afternoon bloating. Made it to 4 PM without unbuttoning her pants. Bathroom activity increased.</p>",
        "gglF6C3to9t_text": "<p><i>\"Started the pack on a Monday. By Friday, the bloating was less. By week three, I'd stopped two of my three IBS medications. My doctor is confused. I don't care.\" —</i> Jen M., neighbor</p>",
        "ggpEU4PGpqv_text": "<p>If your symptoms don't improve, you pay nothing.</p>",
        "ggrmzMKhVj3_text": "<p>Sarah wore the Tavio pack every night. The results followed a pattern Gary would later see repeated across dozens of people:</p>",
        "ggu2IPWT2Cs_text": "<p><i>\"The 3 AM wake-ups stopped by week two. I feel ten years younger.\" — </i>Mike D., Austin, TX</p>"
